AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE JULY
1, 2026]: Sec. 4.5. As used in this chapter, "Class 1 structure" has
the meaning set forth in IC 22-12-1-4.
SECTION 15. IC 36-7-1-4.7 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA CODE
AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE JULY
1, 2026]: Sec. 4.7. As used in this chapter, "Class 2 structure" has
the meaning set forth in IC 22-12-1-5.
